div.h3: I'm a Full-Stack Web Developer💻, Mechatronics Engineer🤖 and Dungeon Master🎲🎲!

div.p: I have a degree in Mechatronics Engineering and a long experience working in Industry: I designed ar-conditioning systems, wrote firmware for programmable logic computer (PLC) modules and eventually moved to the semiconductor industry, where I finished my Masters Degree in Electrical Engineering and went on to become a Semiconductor Packaging Specialist with almost 10 years of experience. However, I have long considered transitioning to a coding career, since I really love it and believe it to be my true vocation. I've always had a knack for programming (be it automating everything with bash scripts and Visual Basic for Applications at work or even my happy time programming with C at the beginning of my career) and finally mustered the courage to leave the comfort zone and dive into something new, so here I am!
(Also, I'm a boardgame and tabletop RPG geek 🤓)
